The paper discusses the architecture and design decisions of a distributed operating system for permissioned blockchains, which involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC), cryptography (cs.CR), and data structures (cs.DS). It also discusses the programming model and implementation aspects, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
